              <img src="/images/customer.svg" class="block m-auto" alt="" />
              <h3 class="text-[1.5rem]">5-star Customer Service</h3>
              <p class="leading-6">
                We’ve got caretakers that actually care about your needs and
                complaints. Your opinions matter to us.
              </p>
